    title: World Mineral Statistics
    description: |-
      The World Mineral Statistics dataset is a compilation of production and trade statistics on a wide range of mineral commodities since 1913.
      However, data prior to 1960 is only available a scanned PDF books, whose content, currently, cannot successfully be extracted programmatically.
    date_published: "2023-01-01"
    title_snapshot: World Mineral Statistics - 1970 onwards
    description_snapshot: |-
      This is a compilation of all the data that is accessible via the BGS web interface, containing imports, exports and production of minerals by country from 1970 onwards.

